OXWM — Credit & Provenance Notice
=================================

OXWM is a fork of MLVWM (Macintosh Like Virtual Window Manager), which
is itself based on FVWM (which is itself descended from Twm). All credit
for the original code and design belongs to the original authors and
contributors listed below. The OXWM fork adds a desktop icon manager
(`oxwm-desktop`), hotfixes, and modern system compatibility on top of
MLVWM.

OXWM retains the original MIT-style freeware license from MLVWM and
the underlying MIT/X11 licenses from FVWM, Twm, and the X Consortium.
See the source file headers and the AUTHORS section of the manual
page for full attribution.

